    "citation" : "Thompson, L.G., E. Mosley-Thompson, M.E. Davis, V.S. Zagorodnov, I.M. Howat, V.N. Mikhalenko, and P.-N. Lin. 2013. Annually Resolved Ice Core Records of Tropical Climate Variability Over the Past ~1800 Years. Science, 340(6135), 945-950. doi: 10.1126/science.1234210",
    "type" : "publication",
